<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="H" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Hue and cry" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Hue and cry,</orth> a clamour in pursuit of an offender: <cit><quote>h., villain, go! fly, run, h.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 92</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 92</bibl> <cit><quote>a h. hath followed certain men unto this house,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.4.556" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 4, 556</bibl></cit>.
